*Declare an integer.

REPORT Z_ABAP101_002.

*We can declare an integer using the 'INT4' data type.

DATA lv_integer TYPE INT4.

*This line declares variable named 'lv_integer' of type 'INT4',
*which is a 4-byte integer in ABAP.
*or

DATA number_of_employees TYPE i.

*We can use these variables to store integer values within ABAP programs.
